thread.title: GE Earnings: What to Watch

author: Thomas Gryta
title: GE Earnings: What to Watch
text:
General Electric Co. is set to report first-quarter earnings before the market opens Friday. Here is what you need to know:
EARNINGS FORECAST: Analysts polled by Thomson Reuters expect earnings of 11 cents a share, compared with adjusted earnings of 21 cents a share during the same period last year.
